# Sajtmaskin Project Rules

## Language
- UI text: Swedish (sidan är på svenska)
- Code & comments: English
- Chat responses: Swedish

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15 (App Router) in `/app` folder
- TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui
- SQLite for persistence
- v0 API for code generation (demoUrl → iframe preview)

## Code Style
- Keep it simple - no over-engineering
- Fix what's asked, don't refactor surrounding code
- Delete old/unused code when replacing
- Run `npm run build` in `/app` to verify changes

## Environment
- Windows 11
- Main code lives in `app/src/`
- Environment vars: only V0_API_KEY is required
- Never commit .env files or API keys

## Process
- Stop any running processes before starting new ones
- Commit frequently with clear messages
- Always verify builds pass before pushing

